<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 03:14:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>韩国和美国启动针对朝鲜军事和网络威胁的年度演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-kick-off-annual-drills-over-norths-military-cyber-threats-2024-08-19/</link><description>韩国和美国周一开始了一年一度的夏季军事演习，旨在加强两国抵御朝鲜武器和网络威胁的联合准备。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-kick-off-annual-drills-over-norths-military-cyber-threats-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>原中国足协副主席因受贿被判有期徒刑11年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/former-chinese-football-vice-president-gets-11-years-jail-bribery-2024-08-19/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社周一援引法院裁决称，中国足协前副主席因受贿罪被判处 11 年有期徒刑，并处罚金 100 万元人民币（139,579.03 美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 01:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/former-chinese-football-vice-president-gets-11-years-jail-bribery-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国需求担忧而缓解，关注中东谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-china-demand-fears-focus-mideast-talks-2024-08-19/</link><description>周一亚洲早盘油价下跌，因对最大石油进口国中国需求疲软的担忧打压市场情绪，而投资者关注中东停火谈判的进展，这可能会降低供应风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 01:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-china-demand-fears-focus-mideast-talks-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>美联储鸽派希望支撑亚洲股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-19/</link><description>由于预期美国经济将避免衰退且通胀降温将启动降息周期，全球股市创下九个月来最好的一周，亚洲股市周一稍事休息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>-南海船只相撞后，菲律宾和中国相互指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-deliberately-collided-with-chinese-vessel-south-2024-08-19/</link><description>菲律宾和中国周一互相指责对方在南海撞船并进行危险的演习，这是两国同意努力缓解紧张局势并处理海上分歧后的最新冲突。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:17:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-deliberately-collided-with-chinese-vessel-south-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国软着陆希望提振新兴市场资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-18/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 21:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-18/</guid></item><item><title>越南最高领导人苏林抵达中国会见习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-top-leader-lam-arrives-china-set-meet-xi-jinping-2024-08-18/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，越南最高领导人苏林周日抵达中国进行为期三天的访问，北京外交部表示，访问期间将包括与国家主席习近平和国务院总理李强的会面。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 03:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-top-leader-lam-arrives-china-set-meet-xi-jinping-2024-08-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国在暂停后发布新的黄金进口配额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-issues-new-gold-import-quotas-after-pause-sources-2024-08-16/</link><description>四位知情人士告诉路透社，尽管金价创历史新高，但中国几家银行已获得央行新的黄金进口配额，预计需求将会复苏。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-issues-new-gold-import-quotas-after-pause-sources-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>李克强：中国将着力促进消费提振经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-focus-boosting-consumption-improve-economy-premier-says-2024-08-16/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国总理李强周五在内阁全体会议上表示，必须大力提振经济，国家将把重点放在刺激消费上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 11:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-focus-boosting-consumption-improve-economy-premier-says-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高额关税影响中国生物柴油生产商寻求新出路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-biodiesel-producers-seek-new-outlets-hefty-eu-tariffs-bite-2024-08-16/</link><description>生物燃料高管和分析师表示，中国生物柴油生产商正在亚洲寻找新的出口渠道，并探索生产其他生物燃料，因为其最大买家欧盟的供应在反倾销关税之前枯竭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 11:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-biodiesel-producers-seek-new-outlets-hefty-eu-tariffs-bite-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>讲解员：什么是锑？中国为何限制锑出口？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/what-is-antimony-why-is-china-curbing-its-exports-2024-08-16/</link><description>中国周四表示，以国家安全为由，将从 9 月 15 日起对部分锑产品实施出口管制，这是北京自去年以来实施的限制战略矿产出口措施的又一举措。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 11:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/what-is-antimony-why-is-china-curbing-its-exports-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>伦敦证券交易所数据显示，7月份中国和沙特阿拉伯是俄罗斯燃料油的最大买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-saudi-arabia-top-buyers-russian-fuel-oil-july-lseg-data-shows-2024-08-16/</link><description>交易商表示，伦敦证券交易所周五公布的数据显示，中国和沙特阿拉伯是俄罗斯 7 月份海运燃料油和减压柴油 (VGO) 出口的最大目的地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 10:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-saudi-arabia-top-buyers-russian-fuel-oil-july-lseg-data-shows-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>恒大境内子公司管理人在会议前向债权人寻求详细信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/evergrande-onshore-units-administrator-seeks-details-creditors-ahead-meeting-2024-08-16/</link><description>官方文件显示，恒大在岸主要子公司的管理人已要求债权人在 11 月 14 日举行的第一次债权人会议之前提供这家陷入困境的房地产开发商所欠债务的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 10:13:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/evergrande-onshore-units-administrator-seeks-details-creditors-ahead-meeting-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称美国导弹系统对中国不构成威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/international-ties-boost-philippines-security-economy-foreign-minister-says-2024-08-16/</link><description>菲律宾周五试图向中国保证，美国中程导弹系统在其领土上的存在不会对中国构成威胁，也不会破坏该地区的稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 08:50:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/international-ties-boost-philippines-security-economy-foreign-minister-says-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国暂时阻止了债券多头的脚步</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-manages-halt-bond-bulls-their-tracks-now-2024-08-16/</link><description>中国债券长期疯狂的涨势已陷入停滞，随着北京方面加大干预力度阻止收益率下跌，投资者纷纷退出，价格下跌，成交量大幅下滑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 08:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-manages-halt-bond-bulls-their-tracks-now-2024-08-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>